    ('thinking-skills', 'ordering-sets', 'Ranking', 'ranking', 'Tests deducing relative rank such as fastest or tallest from comparative clues.', 'Students treat a relative clue as an exact position and over-commit early.', 2, 5, 'single_choice', false, 15),
